## Project Description 🔍
A C++ console application that evaluates and improves your typing skills through:
- Timed typing tests
- Accuracy analysis
- Performance metrics

## Features ✨
### Core Functionality
- **Multi-level Difficulty**
  - 🟢 Easy: Simple sentences
  - 🟡 Medium: Moderate complexity
  - 🔴 Hard: Technical sentences

### Performance Metrics
- 🚀 Typing speed (CPM)
- 🎯 Accuracy percentage
- ❌ Error identification
- 📊 Detailed statistics

## Installation 💻
### Requirements
- C++17 compiler (g++/clang++)
- Make utility (optional)

### Build Instructions
```bash
# Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/typing-test.git
cd typing-test

# Compile with g++
g++ main.cpp -o typing_test -std=c++17

# Or using make (if Makefile exists)
make
